flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Advance Shipping Notice (ASN) arrival or dock scan indicating physical receipt at receiving dock]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Ingest ASN, PO and carrier manifest; schedule receiving window and allocate dock]
  N1 --> N2[Stream: STREAMS - Match ASN to PO, validate quantities, and compute supplier-risk and expected inspection rules]
  N2 --> N3{PB: Agent Team - Agent-guided inspection: present checklist, capture measurements, photos and free-text, and run acceptance heuristics}
  N3 -->|Primary| N4[PB: CWB Lifecycle - Present recommendation to inspector/quality reviewer in CWB for approval or override]
  N4 --> N5[PB: Remote Functions - Execute decision: write acceptance/return/quarantine to S4 and update Blue Yonder WMS; trigger supplier/3PL notifications and create exceptions or expedites in Kinaxis as needed]
  N5 --> N6[PB: UI Screen - Surface results and KPIs: receipt status, quality exceptions, supplier scorecard and open actions]
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Accepted receipts posted to S4 and routed for putaway in Blue Yonder WMS; rejects/quarantines create hold locations and return workflows; partial receipts post partial quantities and trigger replenishment/expedite in Kinaxis; exceptions and supplier notifications recorded in CWB and audit trail.]
  N3 -->|Inspection passes within defined tole...| B1[Auto-accept recommendation; inspector confirms quickly; system posts receipt and triggers putaway]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Receipt posted to S4; WMS putaway initiated; no exception created]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Critical failure (safety/critical spe...| B2[Quarantine material, create return-to-supplier disposition and notify supplier/3PL; generate quality exception and claim]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Material held in WMS quarantine, return workflow created, supplier notified, claims/credit process initiated]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Quantity mismatch or partial damage (...| B3[Partial accept: post received quantity, quarantine remainder, and create expedite/replenishment request in Kinaxis]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Partial receipts posted in S4/WMS; replenish/expedite order created in Kinaxis; exception tracked in CWB]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]